import React,{Component} from "react";
import {LineChart, Line, XAxis, YAxis, CartesianGrid, Tooltip, Legend} from"recharts";
import {Div0,DataDrawItem} from'./sty';
const data = [
    {name: 'Page A', righthand: 4000, lefthend: 2400, amt: 2400},
    {name: 'Page B', righthand: 3000, lefthend: 1398, amt: 2210},
    {name: 'Page C', righthand: 2000, lefthend: 9800, amt: 2290},
    {name: 'Page D', righthand: 2780, lefthend: 3908, amt: 2000},
    {name: 'Page E', righthand: 1890, lefthend: 4800, amt: 2181},
    {name: 'Page F', righthand: 2390, lefthend: 3800, amt: 2500},
    {name: 'Page G', righthand: 3490, lefthend: 4300, amt: 2100},
];
class DataDrawListTrainB extends Component{
    render(){
        return (
                <Div0>
                    <DataDrawItem>
                    <LineChart width={400} height={250} data={data}
                    margin={{top: 5, right: 0, left: 0, bottom: 5}}>
                <XAxis dataKey="name"/>
                <YAxis/>
                <CartesianGrid strokeDasharray="3 3"/>
                <Tooltip/>
                <Legend />
                <Line type="monotone" dataKey="lefthend" stroke="#8884d8" activeDot={{r: 8}}/>
                <Line type="monotone" dataKey="righthand" stroke="#82ca9d" />
            </LineChart>
                    </DataDrawItem>
                    <DataDrawItem>
                    <LineChart width={400} height={250} data={data}
                    margin={{top: 5, right: 30, left: 20, bottom: 5}}>
                <XAxis dataKey="name"/>
                <YAxis/>
                <CartesianGrid strokeDasharray="3 3"/>
                <Tooltip/>
                <Legend />
                <Line type="monotone" dataKey="lefthend" stroke="#8884d8" activeDot={{r: 8}}/>
                <Line type="monotone" dataKey="righthand" stroke="#82ca9d" />
            </LineChart>
                    </DataDrawItem>
                    <DataDrawItem></DataDrawItem>
                </Div0>
        )}}
export default DataDrawListTrainB;
